                  continents, I've enjoyed making new friends everywhere and have shared
                  numerous stories at friends' homes. The vibe of meeting someone in a
                  restaurant or bar is totally different from meeting them at home!
                </p>
              </div>

              <div className="border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-6">
                <h4 className="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-lg">Professional Background</h4>
                <p className="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  I'm a proud MBA graduate from Kellogg, ex-management consultant at BCG,
                  and a serial entrepreneur. My mission is to create authentic,
                  meaningful travel experiences that connect people across cultures.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Section 6: FAQ Accordions */}
      <section className="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
        <div className="container mx-auto px-4">
          <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </h2>
          <p className="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Everything you need to know about dining with us
          </p>

          <div className="max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
            <Accordion type="single" collapsible className="w-full">
              {/* Booking & Logistics */}
              <AccordionItem value="booking">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  How do I book?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  Simple. Browse the website, pick your favorite host, and book directly.
                  The +1 Chopsticks team handles the coordination from there.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="duration">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  How long does the experience last?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  Short and sweet! Travelers usually stay for 2–3 hours. It's mostly for
                  lunch or dinner, though some guests might jump in to help cook if
                  you're up for it.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="cost">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  What does it cost for a guest?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  It depends on the feast! Prices generally range from CNY 200–500 per
                  person. We want to make it affordable yet maintaining the quality.
                  Hosts setting a premium price provide a premium menu and experience.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="schedule">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  What if my schedule changes at the last minute?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  We understand! Experiences can be cancelled for free up to 7 days in advance to respect our hosts' preparation time. Please email us at <a href="mailto:plusonechopsticks@gmail.com" className="text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-semibold">plusonechopsticks@gmail.com</a>
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              {/* Concerns & Safety */}
              <AccordionItem value="language">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  Do I have to speak Chinese?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  Not at all. We do require one of the guests speak conversational English
                  as we will require at least one person in the household to speak the
                  same. Beyond that, an open mind and a warm smile bridge most gaps! We will also prepare a "dining cheat sheet" for you to learn about dining etiquettes in China.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="safety">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  Is the food safe and high quality?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  Absolutely. We aren't trying to list everyone—we are picky! We interview
                  and vet every single host. In some cases, we even send a scout to
                  taste-test the menu first. Quality over quantity, always.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="hosts">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  Who are the hosts? Can they cater my dietary needs?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                  <p>
                    Our diverse community of hosts includes families, couples, and young professionals who share passion of cooking and meeting new people. Whether you're a solo traveler, a couple, or a family, we'll match you with the perfect host.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    No matter whose table you join, one thing is guaranteed: we will carefully accommodate all your dietary needs and restrictions to ensure a perfect meal.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    All hosts are verified by the platform on the readiness to host, including language capability, food style and hygiene, and home environment.
                  </p>
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              {/* For Hosts & Partners */}
              <AccordionItem value="host">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  I'd love to host. What should I do?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  Awesome! Follow the host registration process, upload your pictures and
                  description, and the +1 Chopsticks team will be in touch!
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>

              <AccordionItem value="partners">
                <AccordionTrigger className="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
                  I'm a Travel Agent. Can we work together?
                </AccordionTrigger>
                <AccordionContent className="text-gray-700">
                  We love partners! Please contact us at plusonechopsticks@gmail.com for
                  a partnership proposal.
                </AccordionContent>
              </AccordionItem>
            </Accordion>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Section 8: Becoming a Host */}
      <section className="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 text-white">
        <div className="container mx-auto px-4">
          <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">Love cooking and meeting new people?</h2>
              <p className="text-lg mb-8 text-red-50 leading-relaxed">
